      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat, and a few small dings on the passenger side panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining, and while the car runs and drives, it will likely need some mechanical attention soon for items like brakes or suspension components. It remains a functional, budget-friendly option for someone looking for basic transportation.",
