    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! It's always a bit bittersweet to let a beauty like this go, but I\u2019m looking for someone who\u2019ll love her as much as I have. Honestly, she\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. The paint is glowing, the interior is still crisp, and she drives just as smoothly as the day I brought her home. I\u2019ve taken care of every little detail so you don't have to. It\u2019s rare to find one kept in such stunning shape, and I\u2019d love for her to go to a good home. Come on by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself!",
