      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a masterfully sorted performance icon for the discerning enthusiast. This unit features a high-output twin-scroll turbocharged engine with optimized compression ratios and forged internals for maximum thermal efficiency. The chassis rigidity is unparalleled, benefitting from a factory-spec reinforced subframe and precision-tuned dampers. Power is managed via a seamless dual-clutch transmission paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential, providing surgical-grade throttle response. Every fluid change has been documented using boutique synthetics, and the cooling system has been overhauled with high-flow components to prevent heat soak. This is a zero-fault, turn-key machine with a pristine undercarriage and ceramic-protected finish\u2014truly a museum-grade example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
